{"tid":2260901,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"保安外弛內張 海軍陸戰隊員進駐","createTime":"2020-10-28T02:31:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-28T03:58:12.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"528b3fdb46dcabeda8a261a8e6c850672675c9de","tid":2260901,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T02:31:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/AKBPCRRMSNESXHYCWIRRCLEO5U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FAKBPCRRMSNESXHYCWIRRCLEO5U%2F&d=BCqMRPjRs%2BrlYbPtDS4RDJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=7ce4d9e2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201028%2FAKBPCRRMSNESXHYCWIRRCLEO5U%2F&h=f04ef4f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201028/AKBPCRRMSNESXHYCWIRRCLEO5U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n保安外弛內張 海軍陸戰隊員進駐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kwc08SStb0f3udYFUGVXPM9nVmM=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5UNE3GH7CFA4LHR4PNTMPDFQ4U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fkwc08SStb0f3udYFUGVXPM9nVmM%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5UNE3GH7CFA4LHR4PNTMPDFQ4U.jpg&h=d2b434f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■美國駐港澳總領事館保安嚴密，自聘保安外把守出入口。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】美國駐港澳總領事館位於花園道，一向以保安嚴密見稱，領事館除了自聘保安把守出入口外，領事館內更駐有美國海軍陸戰隊員。昨日在領事館外發生鍾翰林被捕事件，又傳有社運人士想進入領事館尋求庇護，但現場所見，領事館一帶氣氛平靜，保安未見特別加強。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：鍾翰林尋政治庇護前被捕  四人再闖美領館失敗<br />\n<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館正門昨午有至少三名身形高大的保安在場把守，對面的聖約翰大廈。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，保安一度上前向記者查問身份及採訪目的，但未有上前驅趕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n進入需預約 禁帶相機食物<br />\n<br />\n事實上美國駐港澳總領事館保安一向十分嚴密，進入領事館人士除了要先預約，並由指定入口進入及安檢，背囊、相機等電子器材也嚴禁帶入，甚至連水、食物也不能帶入領事館內。美國中央情報局前職員斯諾登曾爆料，指美領館內設有中情局分站；保安局前局長李少光2014年曾透露，回歸後美領館員工多達逾千人，但美領館發言人即澄清，指該館只有140名美國員工及180名香港員工。"},{"pid":"c43af5293dfac7d638ee9d274fdcb98cfdc38566","tid":2260901,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T02:41:24.000Z","msg":"唔係不嬲都有陸戰隊做使館衛隊咩"},{"pid":"2be3c815955e299a3783cbbede2fdee25bc88e58","tid":2260901,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c43af5293dfac7d638ee9d274fdcb98cfdc38566","tid":2260901,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T02:41:24.000Z","msg":"唔係不嬲都有陸戰隊做使館衛隊咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T03:27:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50dd92d1687dd83f8e9d64c01ff70e9db28c938a","tid":2260901,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c43af5293dfac7d638ee9d274fdcb98cfdc38566","tid":2260901,"uid":36441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T02:41:24.000Z","msg":"唔係不嬲都有陸戰隊做使館衛隊咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T03:47:09.000Z","msg":"不嬲都蘋果不嬲唔識扮識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c0a85008e087e8bd39bdaf8f59c2ac87d5d1b8","tid":2260901,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T03:49:33.000Z","msg":"屌, 而家情況同當年北韓難民衝瀋陽日韓使館冇分別"},{"pid":"77c656bb84922a8b88b91e56a4ebf67fedc303e0","tid":2260901,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T03:53:23.000Z","msg":"走去領事館門口捉人  E個獨裁政府已經冇得救"},{"pid":"438a81f8f1bedcb0c62e5f002747ab458ceadad7","tid":2260901,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T03:58:12.000Z","msg":"一隻畜膿打十個marine<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}